videos.description: Zavier Simpson gets the rebound and finds Ignas Brazdeikis for the slam at the other end.
videos.headline: Brazdeikis with a monster dunk in transition

videos.description: Cassius Winston drains a 3 to give Michigan State the lead as a fan with a waffle hat enjoys the moment.
videos.headline: Waffle kid enjoys Winston's 3 to take the lead

videos.description: Cassius Winston finds a cutting Xavier Tillman for the alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Winston with the dime to Tilman for the dunk

videos.description: Michigan State seniors Kenny Goins, and Matt McQuaid get subbed out and kiss the floor while getting a standing ovation.
videos.headline: Michigan State players  kiss the court for senior night

videos.description: Michigan led by 4 at the half, but Michigan State came out hot in the second half for the 75-63 victory.
